OL,3,CSuspended MSP Colin Smyth to appear at
OL,4,CDumfries Sheriff Court later this month
OL,6,FSouth Scotland MSP Colin Smyth has
OL,7,Fbeen told to attend court later this
OL,8,Fmonth after he was charged in
OL,9,Fconnection with alleged possession of
OL,10,Findecent images.
OL,12,FThe 52-year-old was arrested on 5
OL,13,FAugust, prompting his suspension from
OL,14,Fthe Labour Party.
OL,16,FA provisional court date has been set
OL,17,Ffor 24 September at Dumfries Sheriff
OL,18,FCourt.
