OL,3,CSuspended MSP Colin Smyth to appear at
OL,4,CDumfries Sheriff Court later this month
OL,6,FHe is also accused of putting a hidden
OL,7,Fcamera in toilets inside the Scottish
OL,8,FParliament, which he strongly denies.
OL,10,FHis Holyrood pass was deactivated on
OL,11,F28 August.
OL,13,FIn a statement issued last week Mr
OL,14,FSmyth said: "This allegation has come
OL,15,Fas an utter shock and one I strongly
OL,16,Frefute.
