OL,3,CSuspended MSP Colin Smyth to appear at
OL,4,CDumfries Sheriff Court later this month
OL,6,F"For legal reasons, I can't respond to
OL,7,Fspecific matters or speculation, and I
OL,8,Fappreciate there is a process to go
OL,9,Fthrough which I am, of course, fully
OL,10,Fcooperating with. But I sincerely hope
OL,11,Fit can be concluded quickly and fairly.
OL,13,F"The speculation, and the recent
OL,14,Fdecision by the police to publicly
OL,15,Frelease details of their ongoing
OL,16,Finquiries along with my home address,
OL,17,Fhas been devastating and has taken a
OL,18,Fserious toll on my health.
