OL,3,CSuspended MSP Colin Smyth to appear at
OL,4,CDumfries Sheriff Court later this month
OL,6,F"After my address was published with
OL,7,Fno warning to my family, I felt I had
OL,8,Fno choice but to move away to protect
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"That has also meant losing the local
OL,12,FNHS critical support I had been
OL,13,Freceiving for the past few weeks,
OL,14,Fmaking an already difficult time even
OL,15,Fmore distressing.
