OL,6,F"I would therefore ask that the
OL,7,Fprivacy of myself, but above all, my
OL,8,Ffamily and friends, is respected while
OL,9,Fthis matter is resolved. Having this
OL,10,Fhanging over them is especially
OL,11,Foverwhelming."
OL,13,FThe MSP is now listed as an
OL,14,FIndependent on the Scottish Parliament
OL,15,Fwebsite.
